title: The Celts (Time-Life Emergence of Man).pdf
description:
Time-Life | 1974 | Pdf | Eng | 160p | 26 MB

This history book delves into the Celtic culture of ancient times, examining it's rigidly structured social organization, it's religion administered by the Druids, it's eloquent tradition of heroic legends passed down from generation to generation, and it's fantastic art, before it was merged with roman and Germanic customs and traditions
